:GRAPH BURNOUT
:TITLE Worker Burnout
:SCALE
:VAR Accomplishments to Date
:Y-MIN 0
:Y-MAX 5000
:DATASET 
:LINE-WIDTH 4
:SCALE
:VAR Expected Accomplishments Per Week
:Y-MIN 0
:Y-MAX 100
:DATASET 
:LINE-WIDTH 3
:SCALE
:VAR Hours Worked Per Week
:Y-MIN 0
:Y-MAX 100
:DATASET 
:LINE-WIDTH 2
:SCALE
:VAR Energy Level
:Y-MIN 0
:Y-MAX 2
:DATASET 
:LINE-WIDTH 3

:GRAPH Accomplishment
:TITLE Accomplishment
:SCALE
:VAR Accomplishments to Date
:DATASET 
:LINE-WIDTH 1
:SCALE
:VAR Perceived Accomplishments Per Week
:DATASET 
:LINE-WIDTH 1
:SCALE
:VAR Expected Accomplishments Per Week
:DATASET 
:LINE-WIDTH 1

:GRAPH Hours_Worked_
:TITLE Hours Worked
:SCALE
:VAR Hours Worked Per Week
:DATASET 
:LINE-WIDTH 1
:SCALE
:VAR hours worked to date
:DATASET 
:LINE-WIDTH 1
